snippet.title: Deltarune · WM: Pantheon of the Discarded - UNDEREVENT Development Trailer
snippet.description:
Development trailer for "Deltarune•WM: Pantheon of the Discarded", Wandering Makers' new fangame project.

We have refurbished our team's outlook and are now ready to begin a new step! Please look forward to the release of Pantheon of the Discarded.

Watch the full UNDEREVENT 2023: https://youtu.be/ansCGZUhtVk?si=RQH2T44DV2twEQXq

#deltarune #deltaruneWM

Trailer directed by Wandering Makers; edited by UNDEREVENT 2023 Staff members Kasssm and Clazic

You can learn more in our Twitter/X account: https://x.com/wdmakers
Also check our Soundcloud for upcoming music tracks: https://soundcloud.com/wandering-makers
